    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i just feel a bit worried bc it was so sudden... like i've never felt anything like that before. definitely felt like a physical impact. but i really don't want to go to the er if i don't have to, it's like 2am here and i'm just tired. do u think it's worth getting checked out or should i just sleep it off and see how i feel in the morning?",
